      • callWebServiceBackground

        public void callWebServiceBackground(java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> parameters,
                                     boolean isLOV)
                              throws java.lang.Exception
        This method is used to call a webservice using background thread. This is mainly used to optimize the performance Some of the webservice can be pre-call so that when the actual call take place, the result can be used immediately shorten the waiting time of the user
        Parameters:
        parameters - Parameters for the webservice
        isLOV - this property determine if the Web Service is used by LOV or not. If true, then offset and limit will be automatically added to the webservice url
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
